character.name: Tristan
character.physical_description: The character has a large, round, vibrant green head. Its face features two circular red eyes with smaller, circular blue pupils. It has a wide, crescent-shaped red mouth with a thick blue outline, revealing six sharp, white triangular teeth (three on the top jaw, three on the bottom jaw). A crest of seven distinct, sharp, triangular black spikes forms its 'hair' on top of its head. Two black, rectangular, gear-like structures (resembling mallets or hammers with serrated edges) extend horizontally from the sides of the head, just above where the arms begin. Each gear-like structure has a central rectangular bar and two serrated ends. The body consists of a long, rectangular, purple torso. Two thick, rectangular, vibrant green arms extend horizontally from the upper sides of the torso, each ending in a three-fingered hand/claw, also green, with blue outlines defining the fingers. Two thick, triangular, bright orange legs extend downwards from the bottom of the torso. The character stands on two rectangular, vibrant green feet, each with a blue outline and three vertical blue lines on the front, suggesting toes or texture.
character.clothing_description: The character's 'clothing' is integrated into its body structure. Its head and upper chest area are vibrant green. The main body is a distinct, long, rectangular purple section. A single horizontal black line is drawn across the lower third of the purple torso, suggesting a belt or a division. The arms are vibrant green, matching the head. The legs are bright orange and triangular. The feet are vibrant green, matching the arms and head. The black spiky hair and the two black gear-like structures on the sides of the head are integral parts of its appearance, not separate accessories.
key_features: Two red circular eyes with blue circular pupils
Wide red mouth with blue outline and six white triangular teeth (3 top, 3 bottom)
Seven black spiky hair crest on top of head
Two black gear-like structures extending from the sides of the head
Rectangular purple torso with one horizontal black line across the lower third
Two vibrant green, rectangular arms ending in three-fingered hands with blue outlines
Two vibrant green, rectangular feet with blue outlines and three blue lines on the front
character.personality: This character exudes a playful, friendly, and slightly mischievous personality. Its wide, toothy grin and bright, contrasting colors suggest an energetic and enthusiastic demeanor, ready for fun and adventure.
character.drawing_style: The child's art style is cartoonish and bold, characterized by simple geometric shapes (circles, rectangles, triangles) and strong, distinct outlines. It uses solid blocks of vibrant color with minimal shading or detail, typical of a young child's expressive drawing.

suggested_adventures.title: The Great Gear-Monster Gadget Build
suggested_adventures.description: Gear-Grin Gus loves to invent and build! He needs to construct a magnificent flying machine to help his friends reach the highest, juiciest berry bushes in the Whispering Woods. He embarks on a quest to the Sparkle-Scrap Yard to find the perfect, most unusual parts for his grand creation.
suggested_adventures.why_it_fits: This adventure highlights Gus's unique gear-like features, suggesting a knack for mechanics and construction, and his friendly vibe makes him a helpful inventor.

suggested_adventures.title: Rainbow Rumble's Color Quest
suggested_adventures.description: One morning, Gear-Grin Gus (also known as Rainbow Rumble for his vibrant colors) wakes up to find all the colors have mysteriously faded from his favorite forest! He must journey through the land, collecting lost hues and bringing back the vibrant beauty, using his own bright personality to cheer up dull creatures along the way.
suggested_adventures.why_it_fits: This adventure emphasizes the character's own striking and varied color palette, making him the perfect hero to restore color to a world, fitting his cheerful and energetic vibe.

suggested_adventures.title: The Monster Mash-Up Mixer
suggested_adventures.description: Gear-Grin Gus decides to host the biggest, silliest monster party ever! He needs to send out invitations to all his monster friends, prepare funny-shaped snacks, and make sure everyone feels welcome, even the shyest creatures. It's all about fun, laughter, and making new friends!
suggested_adventures.why_it_fits: The character's wide, friendly grin and playful appearance make him an ideal host for a fun-filled monster party, focusing on themes of friendship and inclusivity.

reveal_description:
1.  **HEAD/FACE:**
    *   **Shape, size, color:** Perfectly spherical head, large in proportion to the body. Color is a consistent bright lime green.
    *   **Eyes:**
        *   **Color:** Left eye has a white sclera, a bright red iris, and a black pupil. Right eye has a white sclera, a bright blue iris, and a black pupil.
        *   **Shape:** Both eyes are perfectly circular.
        *   **Size:** Large and prominent, positioned symmetrically on the upper half of the face.
        *   **Outlines:** Each entire eye (sclera, iris, pupil) is outlined with a thick, solid black line. Each pupil contains two white circular highlights: one larger, one smaller, positioned in the upper-left quadrant of the pupil.
    *   **Mouth:**
        *   **Shape:** Wide, open, crescent-shaped smile, curving upwards.
        *   **Color:** The interior of the mouth is a dark purple. The tongue is a bright red, visible at the bottom of the mouth opening.
        *   **Teeth:** Exactly 4 sharp, pointed white fangs are visible on the upper jaw, two on each side of the mouth's center. No lower teeth are visible.
    *   **Any hair/spikes:** Exactly 7 distinct, sharp, spiky protrusions on top of the head. These spikes are solid black and are arranged in a slightly curved line from the left side of the head to the right, with the central spikes being slightly taller.
    *   **Any accessories on head:** Exactly 2 large, cylindrical, dark gray "bolts" or "electrodes" protrude horizontally from the sides of the head, one on each side, positioned slightly above the eye level. Each bolt has exactly 3 distinct, evenly spaced, rectangular notches or grooves on its outer, exposed end. A smaller, dark gray cylindrical connector piece attaches each bolt to the head.

2.  **BODY:**
    *   **Shape, color, proportions:** The torso is a rectangular shape with slightly rounded corners, wider at the bottom than at the top. It is a vibrant purple color. The height of the torso is approximately 1.5 times the height of the head.
    *   **Any patterns, lines, or markings:** Exactly 1 thick, horizontal, solid black band encircles the waist, separating the upper and lower parts of the purple torso. Exactly 2 small, dark gray, cylindrical shoulder connectors are present, one on each side, positioned at the top corners of the torso where the arms attach.
    *   **Clothing details:** Appears to be a simple, sleeveless tunic or shirt.

3.  **ARMS/HANDS:**
    *   **Color:** Bright lime green, consistent with the head color.
    *   **Length, shape:** Arms are cylindrical and proportionate to the body, extending to just below the waist. They have a slight, soft bend at the elbow.
    *   **Number of fingers:** Exactly 3 stubby, rounded fingers on each hand.
    *   **Any accessories:** Exactly 1 thick, solid, smooth light blue cuff or bracelet on each wrist.

4.  **LEGS/FEET:**
    *   **Color, shape:** Legs are cylindrical, straight, and a consistent bright orange color. They are proportionate to the body.
    *   **Any markings or details:** No markings or details on the orange leg sections.
    *   **Feet:** Each foot is large and boot-like. The main body of the shoe is bright lime green. The sole is a distinct, wide, flat band of solid light blue. The front of the shoe is rounded and slightly upturned. Exactly 3 distinct, vertical, slightly curved light blue stripes or indentations are present on the front-top surface of each shoe, extending from the top edge towards the sole.

5.  **UNIQUE FEATURES:**
    *   Asymmetrical eye colors: Left eye is red, right eye is blue.
    *   Exactly 7 black, sharp spikes on top of the head.
    *   Exactly 2 dark gray side head bolts, each with exactly 3 rectangular notches.
    *   Exactly 4 sharp, pointed white fangs visible in the upper mouth.
    *   Exactly 3 fingers on each hand.
    *   Exactly 1 thick, horizontal black band around the waist.
    *   Exactly 1 thick, light blue cuff on each wrist.
    *   Exactly 3 light blue stripes on the front of each shoe.
    *   Overall color palette: Predominantly bright lime green, vibrant purple, bright orange, and light blue
